snippet.title: Fallout Season 2 - Official Teaser Trailer | gamescom 2025
snippet.description:
Watch the Season 2 Teaser Trailer for Fallout, the live-action series based on the Bethesda-developed Fallout game series distributed by Amazon MGM Studios, and Kilter Films produced in association with Bethesda Game Studios and Bethesda Softworks.

Fallout is based on one of the most popular video game franchises of all time and is set 200 years after an apocalyptic event. The story follows the gentle denizens of luxury fallout shelters who are forced to return to the irradiated hellscape their ancestors left behind—and are shocked to discover an incredibly complex, gleefully weird, and highly violent universe waiting for them. The brief teaser trailer depicts Lucy MacLean and Cooper Howard venturing off across the wasteland with New Vegas in the distance, calling back to the famous game location in the franchise.

Fallout Season 2 stars Ella Purnell, Aaron Moten, Walton Goggins, Kyle MacLachlan, Moisés Arias, Frances Turner, and more. The Executive Producers for Fallout Season 2 are Jonathan Nolan and Lisa Joy, alongside Geneva Robertson-Dworet and Graham Wagner also serve as executive producers, creators, and showrunners. Todd Howard, Bethesda Game Studios, executive produces along with James Altman for Bethesda Softworks. 

Fallout Season 2 is premiering in December 17, 2025, with the series also being renewed for Season 3.

#IGN #gamescom2025

snippet.title: Warhammer 40,000: Dawn of War IV Official Announce Trailer | Gamescom Opening Night 2025
snippet.description:
At last, back to war! Warhammer 40,000: Dawn of War IV officially revealed during Gamescom Opening Night Live 2025!

Battle for planet Kronus as Warhammer 40,000's ultimate real time strategy game returns, featuring the largest campaign ever with four distinct factions battling it out in epic, brutal large-scale conflicts. 

Dawn of War IV returns to the legendary RTS series’ roots with satisfying gameplay and a brutal, expanded Sync Kill system. Take command of four Warhammer 40,000 factions, including, for the first time in the Dawn of War series, the Adeptus Mechanicus! Fight through 70+ campaign missions solo or with a friend in a story crafted by legendary Black Library author John French. Immerse yourself in endlessly replayable modes including Last Stand and Skirmish, or take the fight to the world with intense multiplayer combat.

Read more on Warhammer Community: https://www.warhammer-community.com/en-gb/articles/l8pdgqps/warhammer-40000-dawn-of-war-iv/

snippet.title: Sekiro: No Defeat | Official Trailer | Crunchyroll
snippet.description:
Sekiro: No Defeat is coming exclusively to Crunchyroll!

The time is Sengoku.

Japan is fractured into many independent nations entangled in ceaseless war. At the center lies Ashina, a land of sacred earth and ancient mystery. Two decades after Sword Saint Isshin Ashina reclaimed the region in a brutal coup, a new threat emerges from within: The Interior Ministry. Desperate to protect his homeland, Isshin’s grandson Genichiro turns to forbidden powers. The only hope lies in a kidnapped boy — the Divine Heir — and his silent protector: a loyal shinobi known only as Sekiro.

This is the story of a lord and his retainer — and their quest to restore balance to a nation on the edge.

Crunchyroll brings you the latest clips, openings, full episodes, and more from your favorite anime!

he finds a little fire in his heart
thumbs on glass, he writes what no one asked

over a board game he doesn’t get
stubs his toe, lets everyone know
that he can do a push up
(then he’ll do a push up)

Dave, I feel bad for you,
Dave, don’t you know it could be better
Dave,
hmmm

Dave from work does pushups in the dirt
maybe to impress her

Dave079 is an asshole online
and oh, the fire’s gone
(didn’t last that long)

Dave, I feel bad for you,

Dave,
hmmm

snippet.title: Honest Trailers | War of the Worlds (2025)
snippet.description:
It’s the Honest Trailer for War of the Worlds 2025! The version with Ice Cube, Eva Longoria, and all the apps you use to work from home! What would you do if aliens invaded and you were the only person who could stop it? A) Yell at your daughter for eating a muffin? B) spy on the Washington Monument C) Check Fox News or D) All of the above? People have been saying this one isn’t so bad it’s good, but we disagree, this is the most we’ve laughed at a film in years.

What would you like us to make an Honest Trailer for next?

snippet.title: Kingdom Come: Deliverance II - Legacy of The Forge DLC Announce Trailer
snippet.description:
Henry's no longer just a blacksmith's son - he's the master of a legendary forge. Legacy of The Forge, the second story DLC for Kingdom Come: Deliverance II, is coming 9 September 2025.
 
Put your blacksmithing skills to the test as you rebuild a burnt-down forge in the heart of Kuttenberg. Design and customise the workshop, its surroundings, and your private quarters - with upgrades that do more than just look good.
 
Wishlist Kingdom Come: Deliverance II - Legacy of The Forge now.
Kingdom Come: Deliverance II is available on PC, Xbox Series X|S, and PlayStation 5.

LEGO Batman: Legacy of the Dark Knight is the brand-new open world LEGO game from TT Games and Warner Bros. Games, bringing Batman’s 86-year history to life with a mix of iconic DC lore, LEGO humor, and epic action.

🌆 Open World Gotham – Explore famous locations like Ace Chemicals, Wayne Tower, Arkham Asylum, and Gotham Botanical Gardens.
🦇 Playable Heroes – Batman, Jim Gordon, Robin, Nightwing, Batgirl, Catwoman, and Talia al Ghul, each with unique gadgets and combat styles.
😈 Classic Villains – The Joker, Penguin, Poison Ivy, Ra’s al Ghul, Bane, and more.
🚗 Vehicles – Drive legendary Batmobiles and Batcycles.
🎮 Gameplay – New combat system with fluid combos, takedowns, and gadget-based action.
👥 Co-Op – Two-player local couch co-op (no online co-op).
💰 No Microtransactions – 100% complete experience with no in-game purchases.
✨ Bonus Suit – Unlock the Golden Age Batsuit (Detective Comics #27, 1939) by signing up for a free WB Games account.

Platforms: PlayStation®5, Xbox Series X|S, Nintendo Switch™ 2, and PC (Steam & Epic Games Store).
Price/Pre-Order: Not available yet, but wishlisting is open now.

What is Roblox? ROBLOX is an online virtual playground and workshop, where kids of all ages can safely interact, create, have fun, and learn. It’s unique in that practically everything on ROBLOX is designed and constructed by members of the community. ROBLOX is designed for 13 to 18 year olds, but it is open to people of all ages. Each player starts by choosing an avatar and giving it an identity. They can then explore ROBLOX — interacting with others by chatting, playing games, or collaborating on creative projects. snippet.title: Ballad of a Small Player | Official Teaser | Netflix
snippet.description:
Lord Doyle (Colin Farrell) is laying low in Macau – spending his days and nights on the casino floors, drinking heavily and gambling what little money he has left. Struggling to keep up with his fast-rising debts, he is offered a lifeline by the mysterious Dao Ming (Fala Chen), a casino employee with secrets of her own.

However, in hot pursuit is Cynthia Blithe (Tilda Swinton) – a private investigator ready to confront Doyle with what he is running from. As Doyle tries to climb to salvation, the confines of reality start to close in.

BALLAD OF A SMALL PLAYER is directed by Edward Berger (All Quiet On The Western Front, Conclave) and stars Colin Farrell, Fala Chen, Deanie Ip, Alex Jennings and Tilda Swinton.

Watch Ballad of a Small Player, only on Netflix: https://www.netflix.com/title/81692347

About Netflix:
Netflix is one of the world's leading entertainment services, with over 300 million paid memberships in over 190 countries enjoying TV series, films and games across a wide variety of genres and languages. Members can play, pause and resume watching as much as they want, anytime, anywhere, and can change their plans at any time.

snippet.description:
Today I spent all my robux to get the golden goose in Grow A Garden! Make sure you watch the whole video to find out what happens. 

FOLTYN MERCH: https://foltyn.shop/

--Socials--

Discord: https://discord.gg/hqwZhrkqRr

Roblox Group: https://www.roblox.com/groups/1177555...

Roblox Name: TheRealFoltyn

Insta: https://www.instagram.com/foltynn/

Twitter: https://twitter.com/Foltynnn

What is Roblox? ROBLOX is an online virtual playground and workshop, where kids of all ages can safely interact, create, have fun, and learn. It’s unique in that practically everything on ROBLOX is designed and constructed by members of the community. ROBLOX is designed for 13 to 18 year olds, but it is open to people of all ages. Each player starts by choosing an avatar and giving it an identity. They can then explore ROBLOX — interacting with others by chatting, playing games, or collaborating on creative projects. Each player is also given their own piece of undeveloped real estate along with a virtual toolbox with which to design and build anything — be it a navigable skyscraper, a working helicopter, a giant pinball machine, a multiplayer “Capture the Flag” game or some other, yet-to-be-dreamed-up creation. There is no cost for this first plot of virtual land. By participating and by building cool stuff, ROBLOX members can earn specialty badges as well as ROBLOX dollars (“Robux”). In turn, they can shop the online catalog to purchase avatar clothing and accessories as well as premium building materials, interactive components, and working mechanisms.
